  "body": "![Screenshot](https://mapmaking.fr/datapack/img/item_frame_color2.png)\n\n\n# **Color your item frame!**\n\nAdd 16 wool color on item frame\n\n\n**To color:**\n\nBefore v3.0:\nSneak right click with dye on item frame\n\nOn v3.0\nCraft item frame and glow item frame with dye\n\n\n\n**To clear color**\n\nBefore v3.0:\nSneak right click with water bucket on item frame\nOr break item frame\n\nOn v3.0\nNo clear, juste break\n\n\n## Warning\n\n**Older item frame was not compatible with v3.0**",
